\details{
Provides methods for lending assets on the KuCoin margin lending market,
managing purchase (lend) orders, and redeeming lent assets. Inherits from
\link{KucoinBase}.
\subsection{Purpose and Scope}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Loan Market Data}: Query available lending currencies and historical interest rates.
\item \strong{Purchase (Lend)}: Lend assets to the margin pool to earn interest.
\item \strong{Modify}: Update interest rate on existing lending orders.
\item \strong{Redeem}: Withdraw lent assets from the lending pool.
\item \strong{Order Queries}: Retrieve purchase and redemption order history.
}
}

\subsection{Usage}{

All methods except \code{get_loan_market_rate()}
require authentication with Margin permission.
}

